projectGridLines.title: AI (Computer Vision) Intern
projectGridLines.description:
Description: Enhancing the AI-based image processing system. Images of cars, apparel, and non-apparel are provided. The project entails analyzing and segmenting image files based on specific requirements using deep learning and neural network processing skills.

Skill sets: AI/ML, computer vision, neural networks

projectGridLines.title: Full stack internship
projectGridLines.description:
Description: As a full-stack intern, you will contribute to the development and maintenance of both front-end and back-end components of our software applications. You'll gain hands-on experience in various technologies, collaborate with cross-functional teams, and participate in the full software development lifecycle.

Skill sets: Proficiency in JavaScript, HTML, CSS, React or Angular, Node.js, Python or Java, SQL or MongoDB, and strong problem-solving skills.
